name: One Minute Delivery (Rayan)
description:
Controls : 

Arrows to move the "car" around.

Goal : 

Deliver as much packages as possible in under a minute. 

Content : 

The packages spawn randomly, one by one, whenever you pick one up.

The customer has a 50% chance of changing location whenever you deliver a package.
